channel.title: Biggest Challenge Of Feb 2nd 2018 (probably clickbait)!
channel.description:
Recently, the auxy community has changed...
Nevermind that now--A fun challenge instead!
I've been into recreating songs in auxy. I failed miserably, so I'll pass that challenge on to you.
This song: https://soundcloud.com/essential_music/teminite-panda-eyes-high-score-edmcom-exclusive is not only one of my favorite dubstep-y EDM-y songs, but it seems like a nice challenge for you [spoiler]5-bucks-a-month[/spoiler] people.
Feel free to use any drum kits you like as long as it isn't charge or whack or north or frame or dollar or mold or dust or craft.
